國際板球理事會負責審核某國或某群國家的板球隊是否具備對抗賽參賽資格。未具備對抗賽參賽資格的球隊仍可參加賽制相近的{{link-en|國際板球理事會洲際盃|ICC Intercontinental Cup}}（洲際盃）。2014年，國際板球理事會在杜拜舉行會議，並宣佈自2017年的洲際盃板球賽開始，讓盃賽的冠軍與排名最低的對抗賽隊伍進行為期五天的比賽。如果洲際盃冠軍勝出賽事，便能取得對抗賽參賽資格<ref name="bbc-2018-playoff">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/cricket/26973541|title=Ireland and Scotland to get Test chance as ICC approves play-off|publisher=[[英國廣播公司|英國廣播公司]]|date=2014-04-10|accessdate=2015-08-17|language=en|archive-date=2015-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150313153048/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/cricket/26973541|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

辛巴威隊曾於2006年至2011年間因為賽績欠佳而自願暫停參賽資格，直至2011年8月恢復參賽為止<ref name="VOA津巴布韋">{{cite news|url=http://www.voanews.com/zimbabwe/news/Zimbabwe-Cricket-Resume-Test-Play-After-Six-Year-Break-126790218.html|title=Zimbabwe Cricket Side Resume International Test Play After Six Year Break|first1=Marvellous|last1=Mhlanga-Nyahuye|publisher=[[美國之音|美國之音]]|date=2011-08-04|accessdate=2015-08-17|language=en|archive-date=2012-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120131101339/http://www.voanews.com/zimbabwe/news/Zimbabwe-Cricket-Resume-Test-Play-After-Six-Year-Break-126790218.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

愛爾蘭隊曾分別在2009年及2012年向國際板球理事會提交申請，希望成為全權會員並取得對抗賽參賽資格<ref name="espn-cricinfo-ireland-2009">{{cite news|url=http://www.espncricinfo.com/ireland/content/story/432837.html|title=Ireland in hot pursuit of Full Member status|first1=Alex|last1=Brown|publisher=ESPN|date=2009-11-03|accessdate=2015-08-17|language=en|archive-date=2019-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190622154805/http://www.espncricinfo.com/ireland/content/story/432837.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="bbc-ireland">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/cricket/16698328|title=Ireland announce plans to apply for Test status|publisher=英國廣播公司|date=2012-01-24|accessdate=2015-08-17|language=en|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924185259/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/cricket/16698328|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年6月22日，國際板球理事會通過接納愛爾蘭與[[阿富汗國家板球隊|阿富汗]]為全權會員，並賦予兩隊參加對抗賽的資格<ref name="afg-ire-icc">{{cite web|url=https://www.icc-cricket.com/news/422449|title=Ireland and Afghanistan ICC newest full members amid wide-ranging governance reform|publisher=[[國際板球理事會|國際板球理事會]]|date=2017-06-22|accessdate=2017-06-25|language=en|archive-date=2020-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200423094510/https://www.icc-cricket.com/news/422449|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="afg-ire-telegraph">{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/cricket/2017/06/22/ireland-afghanistan-eligible-play-test-cricket-becoming-11th |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170623043036/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/cricket/2017/06/22/ireland-afghanistan-eligible-play-test-cricket-becoming-11th/ |title=Ireland and Afghanistan granted Test status after becoming 11th and 12th full ICC members |agency=[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]] |author=Nick Hoult |date=2017-06-22 |archivedate=2017-06-23 |accessdate=2017-06-25 |language=en |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="afg-ire-sohu">{{cite news|url=http://www.sohu.com/a/151009007_627454|title=阿富汗，爱尔兰面对板球测试D日|author=康康聊体育|website=[[搜狐|搜狐]]|date=2017-06-22|accessdate=2017-06-25|language=zh-cn}}{{Dead link|date=2019年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

== 近況 ==
現時板球對抗賽主要在英格蘭及澳洲受球迷歡迎。然而，近年如[[2020_(板球)|T20板球賽]]的較短賽制開始普及，有論者認為原本投放於板球對抗賽的商業贊助開始轉移到這些需時較短的板球賽事<ref name="bbc-test-cricket-future">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/cricket/23494008|first1=David|last1=Bond|title=Test cricket: Does the oldest form of the game have a future?|publisher=英國廣播公司|date=2013-07-29|accessdate=2015-08-17|language=en|archive-date=2015-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150529061119/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/cricket/23494008|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

